{
  "texts": [
    "A. Human-centered approachGuided by the updated STS design principles, iSTS adopts a human-centered approach.",
    "As outlined in Table 2, each design principle represents and realizes this approach.",
    "Through design principles such as human-centered joint optimization, humanled collaboration, human-led decision-making, and humanguided co-learning/evolving, iSTS aims to achieve humancentered characteristics in AI-based sociotechnical systems.",
    "Moreover, as illustrated in Figure 2, the human-centered approach should be practiced across the four levels of human-AI systems, organizations, ecosystems, and social systems [95], [98].",
    "A hierarchical approachFigure 2 illustrates the hierarchical structure of iSTS across individual human-AI systems, organizations, ecosystems, and social systems."
  ]
}